title: The Bazura Project season 1 S01 Guide to Sinema WebDL (eng subs)
description:
Hosts Shannon Marinko and Lee Zachariah present their "Guide to Sinema", where they explore the six ingredients that make movies the enjoyable scourge on society they are today: Violence, Sex, Money, Profanity, Drugs and Fame. But The Bazura Project is more than just a lesson in cinema history from two film nerds.

Join Shannon and Lee as they unearth the obscure, travel to the future, delve into their subconscious, award the un-awardable, and give a comprehensive DIY guide on all things sinful in cinema
